Info.Title: Dummie the Mummy and the Golden Scarabee
Info.Writer: Tosca Menten (novel), Tijs van Marle, Tijs van Marle
Info.Actors: Julian Ras, Yahya Gaier, Roeland Fernhout, Ton Kas
Info.Plot: In a dull village where nothing ever happens, a boy finds a living mummy in his room. It's the start of an amazing friendship, learning the boy more than any friend could.
